  for multiple functions.
[X] * Edit the exports in 'NAMESPACE', and add necessary imports.
[NA] * Put any C/C++/Fortran code in 'src'.
[NA] * If you have compiled code, add a useDynLib() directive to
  'NAMESPACE'.
[X] * Run R CMD build to build the package tarball.
[X] * Run R CMD check to check the package tarball.

[ ] Read "Writing R Extensions" for more information.

